Delete an existing comment on an owned video
Use this endpoint to delete an owned comment on an organic video posted by an owned TikTok Account.

Note

Comments made by other users cannot be deleted, and can only be hidden. You can hide comments using /business/comments/hide/.
The comment webhook event comment.update enables you to get notifications within five minutes of a comment or reply being deleted from any public video associated with an owned TikTok account. To subscribe to the comment webhook, see Subscribe to the comment update event.
